    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Masonry, corbel-domed huts found from the Medieval period in Ireland and possibly built to house hermit monks.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
